HOH318 which is close to HOH327;
HOH329 which is close to HOH360;
HOH338 which is close to a symmetry_related equivalent of itself;
HOH377 which is close to a symmetry-related equivalent of itself;
HOH482 which is close to a symmetry-related equivalent of itself.

His40 and HIS91 are MONOPROTONATED ON THE EPSILON NITROGEN
HIS57 is monoprotonated on delta nitrogen.
